ASSOCIATED.doc: ASSOCIATED(POINTER) returns .TRUE. if pointer is associated with a target. [F90]

LOGICAL.doc: LOGICAL(L) converts logical value L to specified kind type parameter. [F90]

PRESENT.doc: PRESENT(A) returns .TRUE. if optional dummy argument A was provided. [F90]

TRANSFER.doc: TRANSFER(SOURCE,MOLD) interprets bit pattern of SOURCE as type of MOLD. [F90]
